# YemenWi-Fi Hub Project Overview

YemenWi-Fi Hub is a Laravel 13 marketplace platform for selling Wi-Fi/internet cards and packages in Yemen.

Core domains:
- Auth & Roles
- Users
- Sellers
- Networks
- Inventory/Cards
- Orders
- Wallets & Ledger
- Withdrawals
- Payments
- Admin Operations
- Notifications

This is NOT a simple CRUD dashboard.
The system includes:
- transactional flows
- internal wallet system
- inventory reservation
- financial consistency
- operational dashboards

Always think in:
Product → Domain → Feature → Task

Never attempt giant uncontrolled rewrites.
Work incrementally and preserve architecture consistency.